                        			<h1 itemprop="headline" id="headline" class="headline">How Harvard Business School Has Reshaped American Capitalism</h1>
	                                                <div id="story-meta-footer" class="story-meta-footer">
                                                                                                    

<p class="byline-dateline"><span class="byline" itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"  itemid="https://www.nytimes.com/by/james-b-stewart">By <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/by/james-b-stewart" title="More Articles by JAMES B. STEWART"><span class="byline-author" data-byline-name="JAMES B. STEWART" itemprop="name">JAMES B. STEWART</span></a></span><time class="dateline" datetime="2017-06-04T13:01:24-04:00" itemprop="dateModified" content="2017-06-04T13:01:24-04:00">APRIL 24, 2017</time>
</p>

